Starwind/Steel/Rattrap/Depth Charge




Starwind flew not to far above Zardus and dropped off Rattrap and 
Steel.Starwind fired his forward lasers at Unitron. Rattrap fired 
four blasts at Unitron. Steel fired two plasma shots.







~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Depth Charge flew to the side of Eypon. He pushed Eypons gun down.


Depth Charge:


"He is mine."



Depth Charge pulled out his Rocket laucher and fired two missles.
